The Quadrangle Club.
Chicago University.
Jan 3[[d?] 1902.
My Dear Dr. Taylor,
Your letter of Dec. 28th I found here at Chicago University on my arrival last night. I am telgraphing you this morning, being? quite sure that it is probably too late to be of any service to you--Jan. 13th I am to speak to the Congreational Club in Peoria & Jan. 20th to the Municipal League
